cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and wordnets. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves developing an automatic translation approach. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves disambiguation of word senses, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as machine translation approaches often use neural networks.
